 <span data-ttu-id="46818-103">Quando você recuperar o valor da `RightToLeft` propriedade <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ContextMenu>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MainMenu>, e <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ProgressBar> você obterá o valor de <xref:System.Windows.Forms.RightToLeft> é atribuído.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="46818-103">When you retrieve the value of the `RightToLeft` property from <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ContextMenu>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MainMenu>, and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ProgressBar> you will get the value of <xref:System.Windows.Forms.RightToLeft> you assigned.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="46818-104">Por outro lado, se você estiver derivando sua própria classe de <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control>, e você atribuir um valor de `Inherit` para o <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.RightToLeft%2A> propriedade, o valor retornado será a configuração do <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.RightToLeft%2A> propriedade do controle pai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="46818-104">In contrast, if you are deriving your own class from <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control>, and you assign a value of `Inherit` to the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.RightToLeft%2A> property, the value returned will be the setting of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.RightToLeft%2A> property of the parent control.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="46818-105">Se não houver nenhum controle pai, ele retornará um valor de `No`.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="46818-105">If there is no parent control, it will return a value of `No`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="46818-106">Caso contrário, ele retornará um valor de `Yes` ou `No`, dependendo do valor que você atribuiu para o <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.RightToLeft%2A> propriedade de sua classe derivada.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="46818-106">Otherwise, it will return a value of `Yes` or `No`, depending on the value that you assigned to the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.RightToLeft%2A> property of your derived class.</span></span>  
  
